<h2>Our approach</h2>
<p>Resolve to Save Lives’ approach to salt reduction aims to reduce the global intake of salt by 30% and is based on the World Health Organization’s <a href="https://www.who.int/dietphysicalactivity/publications/shake-salt-habit/en/">SHAKE Technical Package</a>.</p>

<p>We have identified a core set of salt reduction strategies, and work with countries to implement a strategy according to their key sources of salt, complementary efforts and political will.</p>

